    <span class="mx-auto">Pomodoro Method</span>
    <div class="guide-section">
        <h2>Summary</h2>
        <p>
        The Pomodoro Method is a time-management technique that enhances focus and productivity by breaking study sessions into intervals, typically 25 minutes long, separated by short breaks. This method helps maintain high levels of concentration and prevents burnout.
        </p>
