    <div class="guide-section steps">
        <h2>Steps</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Use our Timer in <a href="study-session.ejs">Study Session</a>: Choose a task to work on and set a timer for 25 minutes. Focus solely on this task without distractions.</li>
            <li>Work: Work on the task until the timer rings. If you get distracted, write down the distraction and get back to the task immediately.</li>
            <li>Short Break: Take a 5-minute break after the timer rings. Use this time to relax and clear your mind.</li>
            <li>Repeat: After four Pomodoro sessions, take a longer break of 15-30 minutes to recharge.</li>
        </ul>
